I must tell you.

630
00:24:17,310 --> 00:24:19,310
When Jiuling was a nobody,

631
00:24:19,830 --> 00:24:21,920
your family kept away from her.

632
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:24,280
Now Jiuling is famous all over the world,

633
00:24:24,560 --> 00:24:26,680
but Childe Ning always

634
00:24:26,680 --> 00:24:27,880
comes to see her.

635
00:24:28,430 --> 00:24:30,160
Only saints can stick to

636
00:24:30,350 --> 00:24:32,400
their conscience.

637
00:24:32,830 --> 00:24:33,430
What are you

638
00:24:33,680 --> 00:24:34,880
going to do in the future?

639
00:24:35,310 --> 00:24:36,310
When my mother recovers,

640
00:24:36,760 --> 00:24:37,800
I'll return to the capital city.

641
00:24:38,470 --> 00:24:39,800
Now you're the No. 1 Scholar in the imperial exam,

642
00:24:40,190 --> 00:24:41,560
