644
00:24:45,400 --> 00:24:46,880
I'm afraid it's not so simple.

645
00:24:47,520 --> 00:24:48,350
I thought

646
00:24:48,710 --> 00:24:49,760
it's joyful

647
00:24:49,800 --> 00:24:51,070
