648
00:24:51,710 --> 00:24:52,520
but now it seems

649
00:24:53,110 --> 00:24:54,560
very hard to protect myself

650
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:56,070
in the court.

651
00:24:58,400 --> 00:24:59,470
You haven't become an official,

652
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:01,310
