653
00:25:02,190 --> 00:25:03,190
After studying hard for a decade,

654
00:25:03,560 --> 00:25:05,280
I will have to concentrate on making profits.

655
00:25:05,710 --> 00:25:07,280
It's really disappointing.

656
00:25:08,040 --> 00:25:08,710
In my opinion,

657
00:25:09,190 --> 00:25:10,560
officials should serve the people

