715
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:10,160
If Yunzhao is really engaged to a woman from the merchant family,

716
00:27:10,350 --> 00:27:11,950
it'll be a big joke.

717
00:27:11,950 --> 00:27:13,230
For several generations?

718
00:27:13,710 --> 00:27:15,350
Mrs. Ning knows it

719
00:27:15,800 --> 00:27:17,680
better than I do.

720
00:27:18,280 --> 00:27:18,680
You…

