745
00:28:40,160 --> 00:28:41,040
Unconsciously,

746
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:44,400
I found that I really like you

747
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:45,350
and it's harder for me to control myself.

748
00:28:45,350 --> 00:28:46,000
Jiuling.

749
00:28:46,000 --> 00:28:46,710
Childe Ning,

750
00:28:49,280 --> 00:28:50,040
please don't say so.

751
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:58,310
In the world,

752
00:28:59,800 --> 00:29:01,400
I have few confidants

753
00:29:03,230 --> 00:29:04,470
but you're one.

754
00:29:06,040 --> 00:29:06,760
I know

755
00:29:07,590 --> 00:29:09,190
you've helped me a lot,

756
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:11,190
and I also know your love.

757
00:29:15,190 --> 00:29:15,950
But

758
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:22,430
I can only

759
00:29:24,920 --> 00:29:26,430
refuse you.

760
00:29:32,590 --> 00:29:33,190
I'm sorry.

761
00:29:40,950 --> 00:29:42,710
