765
00:29:50,560 --> 00:29:51,920
which is really good for you.

766
00:29:52,070 --> 00:29:52,920
No need.

767
00:29:54,800 --> 00:29:55,430
I'm not

768
00:29:55,430 --> 00:29:56,920
a stubborn man

769
00:29:57,520 --> 00:29:58,800
and won't give myself up as hopeless.

770
00:29:59,470 --> 00:30:00,110
Moreover,

771
00:30:00,350 --> 00:30:01,520
the love for someone

772
00:30:02,040 --> 00:30:03,070
is a gift from God

773
00:30:03,680 --> 00:30:04,520
but not pain.

774
00:30:06,310 --> 00:30:07,160
Miss Jun, you can be relieved.

