00:30:10,590 --> 00:30:11,230
I'm sorry.

777
00:30:14,760 --> 00:30:15,590
Love

778
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:17,880
is unexplainable.

779
00:30:18,590 --> 00:30:19,590
But I'm

