784
00:30:27,470 --> 00:30:28,760
It's better than let you move forward alone.

785
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:30,430
It's enough

786
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:32,350
to have such a confidant as you

787
00:30:33,310 --> 00:30:33,950
in my life.

788
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:36,710
Remember to take good care of yourself.

789
00:30:37,190 --> 00:30:37,800
Take care.

790
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:39,710
We will

791
00:30:40,070 --> 00:30:41,040
meet again,

792
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,680
but you can't forget me.

793
00:30:52,710 --> 00:30:53,760
Send additional troops here?

794
00:30:55,590 --> 00:30:56,640
