795
00:31:00,160 --> 00:31:01,110
Come on.

796
00:31:02,190 --> 00:31:03,280
Lord Cheng

797
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:04,920
will defeat them.

798
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:07,520
If the late emperor were still alive,

799
00:31:08,350 --> 00:31:09,430
he would absolutely resist and never yield an inch of territory.

800
00:31:10,710 --> 00:31:11,760
But His Majesty is different.

801
00:31:12,280 --> 00:31:13,310
