803
00:31:14,680 --> 00:31:16,400
If Huang Cheng advises him,

804
00:31:18,800 --> 00:31:19,950
I'm afraid they will make peace.

805
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:23,350
I'm going to see His Majesty.

806
00:31:24,040 --> 00:31:24,830
If I can't persuade him,

807
00:31:25,400 --> 00:31:26,350
I'll go back to the North.

808
00:31:27,760 --> 00:31:29,280
Your marriage

809
00:31:29,520 --> 00:31:31,000
