810
00:31:31,190 --> 00:31:32,000
But now

811
00:31:32,350 --> 00:31:33,520
a good marriage has been

812
00:31:33,680 --> 00:31:35,760
completely destroyed by your mother.

813
00:31:36,640 --> 00:31:38,110
We two families are in an embarrassing situation.

814
00:31:38,430 --> 00:31:39,520
So it's impossible for you

815
00:31:39,760 --> 00:31:40,950
to marry Miss Jun.

816
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:43,560
It's not only my mother's fault.

817
00:31:44,040 --> 00:31:45,310
If Miss Jun doesn't like me,

818
00:31:45,430 --> 00:31:46,230
I won't be able

819
00:31:46,590 --> 00:31:47,470
to marry her, either.

820
00:31:48,710 --> 00:31:49,950
Even if you can't marry her,

821
00:31:50,710 --> 00:31:52,160
you can also become old friends

822
00:31:52,470 --> 00:31:53,520
and help each other

823
00:31:53,520 --> 00:31:54,560
in the capital city in the future.

824
00:31:56,430 --> 00:31:57,470
Father, forget it.

825
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,230
I've felt relieved.

826
00:32:02,110 --> 00:32:03,110
Even if you've

827
00:32:03,110 --> 00:32:04,640
