832
00:32:12,950 --> 00:32:13,760
Here you are, Jiuling.

833
00:32:14,040 --> 00:32:15,230
Take my tent with you.

834
00:32:15,590 --> 00:32:16,710
You can use it outdoors.

835
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:17,880
OK.

836
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:20,760
Why not go with a chef?

837
00:32:21,350 --> 00:32:22,710
