838
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:24,110
won't delay your journey.

839
00:32:25,350 --> 00:32:26,920
I go to solve the problem

840
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:28,230
but not to have a trip.

841
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:33,800
How about going with me?

842
00:32:34,430 --> 00:32:35,310
Then I can

843
00:32:35,520 --> 00:32:36,640
talk with you all the way.

844
00:32:37,190 --> 00:32:38,590
I can also talk with Her Ladyship.

845
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:43,070
I'm better at pleasing Jiuling than you are.

846
00:32:43,830 --> 00:32:44,430
Moreover,

847
00:32:45,160 --> 00:32:46,350
you're not as good-looking as me.

848
00:32:49,830 --> 00:32:51,310
When it comes to the appearance,

849
00:32:52,350 --> 00:32:53,520
Childe Ning and His Lordship Zhu

850
00:32:54,070 --> 00:32:55,350
are both good-looking,

851
00:32:55,680 --> 00:32:56,680
and even His Excellency Lu

852
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:58,590
who always found fault with our lady

853
00:32:58,950 --> 00:32:59,830
is also good-looking.

854
00:32:59,830 --> 00:33:00,470
Stop.

855
00:33:02,590 --> 00:33:03,520
Don't talk nonsense.

856
00:33:03,920 --> 00:33:04,920
Clean up the desk for me.

857
00:33:11,520 --> 00:33:12,070
Jiuling,

858
00:33:13,110 --> 00:33:14,760
