861
00:33:21,760 --> 00:33:22,560
In my eyes,

862
00:33:22,560 --> 00:33:23,920
you're always a child.

863
00:33:28,040 --> 00:33:30,070
Why do your words sound strange today?

864
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:33,040
After you leave,

865
00:33:33,949 --> 00:33:35,669
I don't know when I'll see you again.

866
00:33:38,710 --> 00:33:39,280
Jiuling,

867
00:33:39,909 --> 00:33:40,709
after reaching the North,

868
00:33:40,949 --> 00:33:41,949
if you have any difficulties,

869
00:33:42,469 --> 00:33:43,869
